<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .otp-box {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: white;
            background-color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="YOUR_LOGO_URL" alt="Company Logo" width="80">
        </div>
        <h2>Hi {{userName}},</h2>
        <p>To verify your account, please use the one-time password (OTP) below:</p>
        <div class="otp-box">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for<strong>{{OtpValidityDuration}}</strong> and should not be shared with anyone.</p>
        <p>Click the button below to enter your OTP and complete the verification:</p>
        <br>
         {{> button url=verificationUrl text="Verify Now" style="background-color: #2F6A4D; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;"}}
        <p class="footer">If you didnâ€™t request this, please ignore this email or contact our support team.</p>
        <p class="footer"> <a href="mailto:support@gradpal">Support Email</a> | <a href="mailto:support@gradpal">Gradpal Website</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
